(704, 1, '2017-10-04 12:25:19', '2017-10-04 12:25:19', 'Nielson recently produced a report on the state of radio as a marketing channel concluding that there is that evidence that money spent on radio is money well spent. With their single source purchaser data capability they are able to determine marketing effectiveness in radio. Sounds great but expensive. Canât we just ask our listeners directly?', 'Reaching Listener-Level Measurement in Radio', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '25-revision-v1', '', '', '2017-10-04 12:25:19', '2017-10-04 12:25:19', '', 25, 'http://202.164.49.132:4259/sidemarketing/index.php/2017/10/04/25-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0);
